news.title: Another profitable cannabis cannibis producer: Greenway green house posts first results since market debut
news.description: Greenway Green house (CSE.GWAY) released its first quarter financial statements since hitting markets in september. Revenue came in at C$1.50 millions ($908,092) with gross profit before fair value adjustments at $C532.263. The company however reported a net loss C$1...
